      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "roundness": null,
      "text": "100K workflows · 1M runs/day\n≈ 10 new runs/sec average\n\nIngest QPS: baseline 10 · peak 100 (10×)\nThroughput: ~600 concurrent if ~1 min/run\nPeak concurrent target: up to ~60K\n\nDesign for disk I/O, concurrency, reliability.",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 5,
