    {
      "angle": 0,
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "_dw-PWBMa0LRu1mlDo4tB"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "seed": 1966215847,
      "versionNonce": 1066501447,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1783746993997,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "id": "P-pk6czwrrWdMKKOuNi4n",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -518.3191586396724,
      "y": 2255.213505921747,
      "width": 680,
      "height": 131.25,
      "strokeColor": "#0F172A",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "roundness": null,
      "text": "Is the system read-heavy or write-heavy? Does that change storage choice?\nWrite-heavy — we log state transitions and (later) node traces, plus historical/analytics\ndata.\nEntity relationships still matter though.\n\n→ Postgres for OLTP\n→ ClickHouse for OLAP (logs / traces / analytics)",
      "fontSize": 15,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Is the system read-heavy or write-heavy? Does that change storage choice?\nWrite-heavy — we log state transitions and (later) node traces, plus historical/analytics data.\nEntity relationships still matter though.\n\n→ Postgres for OLTP\n→ ClickHouse for OLAP (logs / traces / analytics)",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "version": 107,
      "index": "b6j"
    },
