    {
      "angle": 0,
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "VwJlPSEr7cAa9i0NTdxHL"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "seed": 1865024512,
      "versionNonce": 509590528,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1783934588389,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "type": "text",
      "id": "SDadEwlmAhkW78wR95rsx",
      "x": 2549.4664695256834,
      "y": 3226.327546286774,
      "width": 720,
      "height": 150,
      "strokeColor": "#0F172A",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "roundness": null,
      "text": "Core concepts:\n• Workflow — orchestration code (deterministic): what runs next, branches, waits\n• Activity — side effects: HTTP, Composio, sandboxed JS, DB writes\n• Worker — polls Temporal, runs workflows + activities\n• Event history — durable log; enables crash recovery via replay\n• Task queues — how work is routed to workers\n\nMental model: durable brain + history; your node executors become Activities.",
      "fontSize": 15,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Core concepts:\n• Workflow — orchestration code (deterministic): what runs next, branches, waits\n• Activity — side effects: HTTP, Composio, sandboxed JS, DB writes\n• Worker — polls Temporal, runs workflows + activities\n• Event history — durable log; enables crash recovery via replay\n• Task queues — how work is routed to workers\n\nMental model: durable brain + history; your node executors become Activities.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "version": 81,
      "index": "b8l"
    },
