      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "cxkoYF1X5Fm9lEWrSFu1b"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "seed": 167394304,
      "versionNonce": 1102939136,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1783935062425,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "type": "text",
      "id": "ivLk6iMAKAqfzaqQoP8pg",
      "x": 3777.5320762891033,
      "y": 2938.951390461154,
      "width": 720,
      "height": 206.25,
      "strokeColor": "#0F172A",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "roundness": null,
      "text": "First decide if the workflow builder is the core product, or just an internal tool.\n\n• Core product (like Sim / Gumloop / Orchex)\n  → don’t outsource the orchestration brain.\n  → prefer Queues + Workers, with Durable Lambda only for isolation of untrusted function code.\n\n• Internal tool on existing AWS\n  → Step Functions is fine — buy durability, ship faster.\n\n• Internal tool that needs a strong long-running execution layer\n  → Temporal is a strong fit.",
      "fontSize": 15,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "First decide if the workflow builder is the core product, or just an internal tool.\n\n• Core product (like Sim / Gumloop / Orchex)\n  → don’t outsource the orchestration brain.\n  → prefer Queues + Workers, with Durable Lambda only for isolation of untrusted function code.\n\n• Internal tool on existing AWS\n  → Step Functions is fine — buy durability, ship faster.\n\n• Internal tool that needs a strong long-running execution layer\n  → Temporal is a strong fit.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "version": 36,
      "index": "bBa"
    },
