      "type": "text",
      "id": "inHVqoX4oXtobWWkKDGxi",
      "x": 3777.5320762891033,
      "y": 5847.201390461154,
      "width": 720,
      "height": 225,
      "strokeColor": "#0F172A",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "roundness": null,
      "text": "Decision rule:\n\n1) Workflow builder is the CORE PRODUCT\n   → Queues + Workers (+ Durable Lambda for function isolation only)\n\n2) Internal tool, already on AWS, moderate needs\n   → AWS Step Functions\n\n3) Internal tool, need strong long-running execution\n   → Temporal\n\nOrchex = case (1). Own orchestration; rent sandbox.",
      "fontSize": 15,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Decision rule:\n\n1) Workflow builder is the CORE PRODUCT\n   → Queues + Workers (+ Durable Lambda for function isolation only)\n\n2) Internal tool, already on AWS, moderate needs\n   → AWS Step Functions\n\n3) Internal tool, need strong long-running execution\n   → Temporal\n\nOrchex = case (1). Own orchestration; rent sandbox.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "version": 36,
      "index": "bCq"
    },
