      "width": 720,
      "height": 18.75,
      "strokeColor": "#0F172A",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "roundness": null,
      "text": "So Step Functions isn’t cheating — it’s buying the orchestrator. You just shouldn’t buy the orchestrator if the orchestrator is your product?",
