      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "So Step Functions isn’t cheating — it’s buying the orchestrator. You just shouldn’t buy the orchestrator if the orchestrator is your product?",
