      "id": "1fyS0oVSmRfxHp-84hX86",
      "x": -1931.87341796672,
      "y": -6.089456846371377,
      "width": 720,
      "height": 262.5,
      "strokeColor": "#0F172A",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "roundness": null,
      "text": "• Core product (like Sim / Gumloop / N8N / Zapier)\n\n→ we don’t outsource the orchestration brain.\n\n→ prefer Queues + Workers, with Durable Lambda only for isolation of untrusted function code.\n\n• Internal tool on existing AWS\n\n→ Step Functions is fine — buy durability, ship faster.\n\n• Internal tool that needs a strong long-running\nexecution layer\n\n→ Temporal is a strong fit.",
      "fontSize": 15,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "• Core product (like Sim / Gumloop / N8N / Zapier)\n\n→ we don’t outsource the orchestration brain.\n\n→ prefer Queues + Workers, with Durable Lambda only for isolation of untrusted function code.\n\n• Internal tool on existing AWS\n\n→ Step Functions is fine — buy durability, ship faster.\n\n• Internal tool that needs a strong long-running\nexecution layer\n\n→ Temporal is a strong fit.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "version": 306,
      "index": "bHn"
    },
